[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    600[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ) -> dict:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    601[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    602[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Full wound measurement pipeline: validate, calibrate, segment, measure, store.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    603[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    604[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Args:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    605[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         image: PIL Image of the wound with reference marker
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    606[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         patient_id: Patient identifier
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    607[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         wound_id: Unique wound identifier
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    608[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         wound_location: Anatomical location
