[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    670[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     print(f"  Circularity: {measurements['circularity']}")
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    671[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    672[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Step 5: Store and compute trajectory
